Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:22.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
